org.simplecorporation.myengine.core.input

Class KeyboardInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.simplecorporation.myengine.core.input.KeyboardInput

  • public class KeyboardInput
extends java.lang.Object
    The KeyboardInput class that contains all of the key codes for the keyboard used by MyEngine when calling events and also holds boolean values for each key that can be statically accessed which are equal to true when that key is currently pressed (Down).

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static int convertKeyCode(int keyCode)
      This method checks the current settings and then converts a key code from a format into the format used by MyEngine as defined in this class.
      static boolean isKeyDown(int keyCode)
      This method can be used to check if a specific key is currently pressed
      static void onKeyPressed(KeyboardEvent event)
      This method is called automatically when a key is pressed and sets the appropriate value for that key
      static void onKeyReleased(KeyboardEvent event)
      This method is called automatically when a key is released and sets the appropriate value for that key
      static void setKeyDown(int keyCode, boolean keyDown)
      This method uses a keyCode taken from this class and a boolean value representing whether that key should be 'down' and sets the appropriate value for that specific key.

        Returns:
        A boolean value stating whether that key is currently pressed (Down)

      • convertKeyCode

        public static int convertKeyCode(int keyCode)
        This method checks the current settings and then converts a key code from a format into the format used by MyEngine as defined in this class. If OpenGL is equal to false, it will use KeyEvent key codes and then convert them into the MyEngine format however, if OpenGL is equal to true it will convert the keyCode assuming it is a code from the Keyboard class in LWJGL.
        Parameters:
        keyCode - An integer value representing the key code to convert
        Returns:
        An integer value representing the MyEngine key code taken from this class.

              boolean keyDown)

        Parameters:
